A dingo puppy is a new monster in [SLASH'EM](/wiki/SLASH%27EM "SLASH'EM"). Aside from not being a [domestic animal](/wiki/Domestic_animal "Domestic animal"), it is identical to a [little dog](/wiki/Little_dog "Little dog"). If you do manage to tame one, it can grow up to become a [dingo](/wiki/Dingo "Dingo"), and eventually a [large dingo](/wiki/Large_dingo "Large dingo").

## Strategy

While not a huge threat, these can extinguish some of the weaker starting roles in SLASH'EM. [Ranged weapons](/wiki/Ranged_weapon "Ranged weapon") are advised if you are low on HP.

A dingo puppy:

  • has no hands.
  • is an animal.
  • is carnivorous.
  • is normally generated hostile.
  • can be seen through infravision.
  • does not appear in Gehennom.
Reference SLASH'EM_0.0.7E7F2/monst.c#line428

Strategy

While not a huge threat, these can extinguish some of the weaker starting roles in SLASH'EM. Ranged weapons are advised if you are low on HP.
